[_______________]{$ans2}   ft/sec. [@ AnswerFormatHelp("numbers") @]*

END_PGML

#################
BEGIN_PGML_HINT

The velocity of the object can be found by finding the derivative of its position function. [`v(t)=s'(t)`].

END_PGML_HINT
